snippet.title: Overboard VR Trailer
snippet.description:
Get it now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1144080/Overboard/

A ridiculous VR game about fighting bloodthirsty and increasingly deadly sharks using makeshift weapons. Elevate the battle from the open ocean to the skies, and even space, as the sharks will stop at nothing to devour a tasty human.

Join the community discord: https://discord.gg/v3AuK92
